These codes are used for analysis after PLSR correction applied.

Following matlab codes are uploaded.

PLSR_data_all.m        - apply PLSR for activity or FC. This code needs dependency from West et al., 2024 (github link below).
https://github.com/west0883/calcium_imaging_of_externally_and_internally_driven_locomotion

PLSR_ddf_all.m         - average sensory-driven activity for each behavior periods.
PLSR_FC_all.m          - average sensory-driven FC for each behavior periods.
PLSR_ddf_merge_all.m   - stack sensory-driven activity data for each track across animals.
PLSR_FC_merge_all.m    - stack sensory-driven FC data for each track across animals.
